{"tid":507274,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"自小嚮往失明 倒通渠水落眼整盲自己","createTime":"2017-12-23T05:20:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-23T07:01:05.000Z","uid":36097,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c202c98d485ebc78cbd849bd5c8d91f269ac1b76","tid":507274,"uid":36097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T05:20:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20151001/large/1443703644_be57.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20151001%2Flarge%2F1443703644_be57.jpg&h=69ee0f35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n夢想，每個人都曾擁有！美國北卡羅來納州一名女子從小的人生目標，竟然希望做一名瞎子，更千方百計令自己失明。<br />\n<br />\n30歲舒平（Jewel Shuping）說自童年起已想失明，「當我三至四歲時，我母親發現我晚上在廳上踱步，六歲時我每每想到失明，就令我感到舒服。」<br />\n<br />\n當她母親告訴她望着太陽會傷害眼睛後，便刻意凝望太陽數小時，18歲那年起，更會戴墨鏡及持拐杖行路。2006年，21歲的她找到一位心理醫生願意幫她變盲，最初醫生用舒平從加拿大拿回來、有麻木效果的眼藥水滴眼，然後變成用通渠水。<br />\n<br />\n舒平承認過程非常痛苦，「我的眼睛尖叫，一些通渠水更滴落面頰，灼傷我的皮膚，但我想到『我會失明』，一切都不成問題。」初時幾次滴眼後都不成功，她說早上醒來發現還看得見電視就深感失望。<br />\n<br />\n最終半年後她達成「心願」，她失明了，左眼由於角膜嚴重受損而要摘除，右眼則有青光眼、白內障。她的家人知道舒平的失明「不是意外」後，不肯原諒她，但她坦言不後悔，更想幫助其他失明者獨立生活。<br />\n<br />\n舒平其實是患上「身體完整認同障礙」（Body Integrity Identity Disorder，BIID），她呼籲患者要尋求專業意見，不要學她那樣自殘身體。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》"},{"pid":"e3b162a16e42419573edc9894afca57ffa362787","tid":507274,"uid":25899,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T05:23:55.000Z","msg":"弱撚智 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"981b76b3c0a5afad9c72816e9bf923f799f778d3","tid":507274,"uid":40272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T05:24:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CjTrOv6UoAARoCP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCjTrOv6UoAARoCP.jpg&h=35ec9b7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d4ca5f9bfd983cfba5c5268ec894c83c394e5fb4","tid":507274,"uid":188,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T05:28:43.000Z","msg":"包住雙眼囉 又唔洗又話痛又乜乜乜"},{"pid":"1acd8d950617c2c9f2f46ccd6259ff88de2e5ce7","tid":507274,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"981b76b3c0a5afad9c72816e9bf923f799f778d3","tid":507274,"uid":40272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T05:24:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CjTrOv6UoAARoCP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCjTrOv6UoAARoCP.jpg&h=35ec9b7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T05:35:54.000Z","msg":"眼球可以拎番"},{"pid":"fc4eb1f799e2738656594f37106f0a431e3d6ca5","tid":507274,"uid":32810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T05:36:31.000Z","msg":"天下無敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e388d61c28964849e1cce4e9b05ac6e57c14fb7b","tid":507274,"uid":121711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T05:38:09.000Z","msg":"on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5619be7f15994463e15239e1bd124a36e0451c4a","tid":507274,"uid":37258,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T05:47:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20151003/19319372\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20151003%2F19319372&d=YMjKz3cQ%2Fky9YqE0tBko1gHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=19dbdaa0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20151003%2F19319372&h=2b5542a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20151003/19319372</a><br />\n屌回帶西 2015年都夠膽po上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ce1075239d65e7ca0cbb3327d27cf05b88b1c90","tid":507274,"uid":275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"